&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Solution:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Let the number be &amp;#39;x&amp;#39;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Number when multiplied by &lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(\frac{7}{8}\)&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;= &lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(\frac{7}{8}\)&lt;/span&gt;x&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Number when multiplied&amp;nbsp;by&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(\frac{17}{8}\)&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(\frac{17}{8}\)&lt;/span&gt;x&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;According to the question:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(\frac{17}{8}\)&lt;/span&gt;x - &lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(\frac{7}{8}\)&lt;/span&gt;x = 30&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;rArr; 17x - 7x = 30&amp;nbsp;&amp;times;​ 8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;​​​&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; 10x = 240&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; x = 24&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;there4; the&amp;nbsp;actual number was &amp;#39;24&amp;#39;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence the correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;24&amp;quot;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The given series:&amp;nbsp;720, 120, 24, 8, 2, 1, 1&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From left to right, the second letter is one-sixth of the first, the third letter is one-fifth of the second, and so on.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/21/07/Numser67236.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 282px; height: 127px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thus, &lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;6&amp;#39; &lt;/strong&gt;will come in place of &lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;8&amp;#39; &lt;/strong&gt;in the number series to make the series correct.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;8&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; is the wrong term in the series.&lt;/p&gt;

