&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Statement:&lt;/strong&gt; The opposition party criticized the government over the increased unemployment rate.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Conclusions:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I. Only the government is responsible for the increased unemployment rates.&lt;/p&gt;

